'''扁桃苷'''（Amygdalin，源自[[希腊语|希腊语]]“[[扁桃|扁桃]]”{{lang|el|ἀμυγδάλη ''amygdálē''}} ），又名「苦杏仁苷」 ，是可從許多植物中發現的一種有毒的[[氰苷|氰苷]]，但最常見於杏、苦杏仁、蘋果、桃及梅子等植物的種子中，易形成水合物。是1803年{{le|皮埃尔-让-洛比克|Pierre Jean Robiquet}}<ref>{{cite web
 |title=A chronology of significant historical developments in the biological sciences 
 |work=Botany Online Internet Hypertextbook 
 |publisher=[[University_of_Hamburg|University of Hamburg]], Department of Biology 
 |date=2002-08-18 
 |url=http://www.biologie.uni-hamburg.de/b-online/e01/geschichte.htm 
 |accessdate=2007-08-06 
 |deadurl=yes 
 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070820063617/http://www.biologie.uni-hamburg.de/b-online/e01/geschichte.htm 
 |archivedate=2007-08-20 
}}</ref>与A. F. Boutron-Charlard从[[扁桃|扁桃]]的种子中分离出的一种[[糖苷|糖苷]]。[[尤斯图斯·冯·李比希|李比希]]与[[弗里德里希·维勒|维勒]]于1830年研究了这一物质。扁桃苷也存在于其他的[[李属|李属]]植物，包括[[杏|杏]]和黑樱桃中<ref>{{cite journal en|author=Swain E, Poulton JE |title=Utilization of Amygdalin during Seedling Development of Prunus serotina |journal=Plant physiology |volume=106 |issue=2 |pages=437–445 |pmid=12232341 |pmc=159548 |url=http://www.plantphysiol.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=12232341 |doi=10.1104/pp.106.2.437|date=October 1994}}</ref>，也存在於[[枇杷|枇杷]]的葉、果和核裡。恩斯特·T·克雷布斯（Ernst T. Krebs）曾将这一物质命名为“维生素B17”，并认为可以治疗[[癌症|癌症]]，但随后的研究证明这一物质并不具有上述功效。<ref>{{cite journal en|author=Ellison NM, Byar DP, Newell GR |title=Special report on Laetrile: the NCI Laetrile Review. Results of the National Cancer Institute's retrospective Laetrile analysis |journal=N. Engl. J. Med. |volume=299 |issue=10 |pages=549–52 |pmid=683212 |date=September 1978}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en|author=Moertel CG, Ames MM, Kovach JS, Moyer TP, Rubin JR, Tinker JH |title=A pharmacologic and toxicological study of amygdalin |journal=[[Journal_of_the_American_Medical_Association|JAMA]] |volume=245 |issue=6 |pages=591–4 |pmid=7005480 |doi=10.1001/jama.245.6.591 |date=February 1981}}</ref><ref name=Moertel82>{{cite journal en |author=Moertel CG, Fleming TR, Rubin J, ''et al.'' |title=A clinical trial of amygdalin (Laetrile) in the treatment of human cancer |journal=[[New_England_Journal_of_Medicine|N. Engl. J. Med.]] |volume=306 |issue=4 |pages=201–6 |pmid=7033783 |doi=10.1007/s00520-006-0168-9 |url=http://content.nejm.org/cgi/content/abstract/306/4/201 |date=January 1982 |access-date=2009-08-13 |archive-date=2003-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030421104145/http://content.nejm.org/cgi/content/abstract/306/4/201 |dead-url=no }}</ref>學界也不認為苦杏仁苷是一種[[維生素|維生素]]，因為苦杏仁苷並不符合維生素的定義。<ref name=CaCancer>{{cite journal |author=Lerner IJ |title=Laetrile: a lesson in cancer quackery |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_acta-physiologica-pharmacologica-et-therapeutica_1981_31_2/page/91 |journal=CA Cancer J Clin |volume=31 |issue=2 |pages=91–5 |year=1981 |pmid=6781723 |doi=10.3322/canjclin.31.2.91}}</ref>

== 化学性质 ==
扁桃苷的提取，可用扁桃或[[杏仁|杏仁]]在[[乙醇|乙醇]]中加热，之后蒸发[[溶剂|溶剂]]并添加[[乙醚|乙醚]]，即可得到细小的白色扁桃苷晶体。李比希和沃勒发现扁桃苷分解时生成三种产物：糖类、[[苯甲醛|苯甲醛]]和[[氢氰酸|氢氰酸]]<ref>{{cite journal en
 | title = Ueber die Bildung des Bittermandelöls
 | author = F. Wöhler, J. Liebig 
 | journal = Annalen der Pharmacie
 | year = 1837
 | volume = 22
 | issue = 1
 | pages = 1–24
 | doi =10.1002/jlac.18370220102
}}</ref>。之后的研究表明，硫酸催化下扁桃苷分解成[[葡萄糖|葡萄糖]]，[[苯甲醛|苯甲醛]]和[[氢氰酸|氢氰酸]]，而[[盐酸|盐酸]]使之分解为[[扁桃酸|扁桃酸]]，[[葡萄糖|D-葡萄糖]]和[[氨|氨]]。<ref>{{cite journal en
 | title = The hydrolysis of amygdalin by acids. Part I
 | author = J. W. Walker, V. K. Krieble
 | journal =  [[Journal_of_the_Chemical_Society|Journal of the Chemical Society]]
 | year = 1909
 | volume = 95
 | issue = 11
 | pages = 1369–77
 | doi =  10.1039/CT9099501369
}}
</ref> 

在[[酶|酶]]的催化下扁桃苷有两种分解：[[麦芽糖酶|麦芽糖酶]]使之部分分解，生成[[葡萄糖|D-葡萄糖]]与扁桃腈葡糖苷（C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>CH(CN)O·C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>11</sub>O<sub>5</sub>），一种苯乙腈葡糖苷的同分异构体。[[扁桃酶|扁桃酶]]则可使之分解为[[苯甲醛|苯甲醛]]、[[氰化物|氰化物]]和两分子葡萄糖。这一反應出现在[[扁桃|苦扁桃]]中，导致苦扁桃中通常含有自由的[[苯甲醛|苯甲醛]]与[[氰化物|氰化物]]。

